<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;I was caught.  Once.  While I was still learning magic.  It wasn't easy getting out, either.  I nearly died that time.  But that incident was what made me such a powerful mage.  Dark lords aren't as smart as they think.  The very idea that a clan could go without their golden leader!  Hunters prefer to go after golds and other metallics.  Iris is lucky to be green.  Hunters like gold ones best because we glitter.  It's getting to become a challenge to go after me because I'm clan leader.  And because of this-&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
