<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Half of their group comes after me so I get most of them with lightning or fireballs or whatever spell I decide to use.  The other half gets to survive until the next go.  Of course, I only need to kill one to make them leave so the rest are traumatized for life after trying.  Ever wonder how our wings turned red?  It's because of the way we used to take out Hunters.  The blood stained our wings and the darker the shade, the higher the status.  But since I hatched with wings this dark they follow me.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
