<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;And on the subject of my little pet, My saving her was completely by accident.  I was trying to save my own hide and happened to step on her tail.  When the Hunters ran off she just clung to my foot and asked to come with me.  But now she's perfectly safe.  I suppose you could say she was in the wrong place at the right time.  But she's been with me ever since.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
