<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Flaming idiots.  The Hunters are coming to find me.  I think they should be around in a week or two.  Avoid the village then and bring Iris with you unless you want to come here and watch me do what I do best.  If you're a dragon, of course.  I'll still be here.  I know they followed me and if they want to risk being incinerated this year, they'll come.  Rest assured, they won't get me.  Or you for that matter.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
