IC: *For a few seconds, all Kyla can do is stare. This is a whole new world that has been opened up to her, just by talking to the ruby-winged, golden queen, and now she's feeling more than a little disorientated. It's all so unreal... but familliar in parts, too. Merenths cry wouldn't have alarmed her, if it hadn't been so loud and her new friend not so large in comparison... After all, Kyla's got remembered nights hidden far away, strange, moaning sobs echoing through the dark as she washed her scales clean in the river, tried to forget. As far as she can work out, it's a sign of a dragon in mourning... just like people cry. But it <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>is</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> real, it must be, because the rock is hot and rough under her feet, Merenth's breath is coming out in heavy, slow heaves beside her, and in front a sky blue dragon is staring back at her with equal apparent disbelief... oops!*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;I'm sorry....&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> *she mutters apoligetically* <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;I didn't expect to hear... it's just... we're supposed to be really rare....&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*The silence trails on, a little uncomfortingly. Still half-numbed by surprise, it slowly dawns on the small dragon that he probably wants to hear her <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>name...</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Umm, my name's Kyla. Nice to meet you?&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*She does her best to smile.* <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>~The stars shine only in darkness~ </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=663399><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bdragonise.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lythiaren>Lythiaren</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.neopets.com/smileys/eyrie.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font Color=red>~Admin Dragon!~<br>
