<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:skyblue;">&quot;I know, I know.  You were lucky you were alonse first time you changed.  I <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>was</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a performer in my village and my first change was on the stage.  Once they realized what happened I had to fly off.  There were Hunters there that night and I barely got away from town without getting caught.  And before you ask, I can read minds too.  It's hard to hide thoughts from anything that has scales and flies on ruby wings.  I found that out when I joined the clan.&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
